summary:
This is the first time I&rsquo;m writing something on a blog of my own, guys. I must say that I never knew composing a blog using Markdown was really possible. I had set up so many blogging platforms over the years using every frontend and backend stuff I learned, but as Da Vinci had correctly said:
&ldquo;Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.&rdquo;
So, here we are, I&rsquo;m using this neat little static site generator called Hugo to build my blog finally.
